      "created": 1774790234,
      "updated": 1774790248
    },
    {
      "id": "69c9265a00000000003c8294",
      "text": "[LLMによるヨイショ]というタグを貼って回った",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1774790234,
      "updated": 1774790437
    },
    {
      "id": "69c9272500000000003c829a",
      "text": "生成AIのシカファンシーという言葉がすでにあるならそちらに変えたほうがいいかな",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1774790437,
      "updated": 1774790453
    },
    {
      "id": "69c926bf00000000003c8296",
      "text": " [LLMによるヨイショ]のほうが自己言及的でわかりやすい",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1774790335,
      "updated": 1774790433
    },
    {
      "id": "69c926d000000000003c8297",
      "text": " シカファンシーだと想像できない",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1774790352,
      "updated": 1774790358
    },
    {
      "id": "69c9274b00000000003c829d",
      "text": "  いいえ、Sychophnacyで慣れてる人(Sychophancyという言葉にイメージをすでに紐づけられた人)には想像できる",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1774790476,
      "updated": 1774790860
    },
    {
      "id": "69c926d600000000003c8298",
      "text": " シカファンシー・Sycophancyという言葉を使うと、英語圏の情報に経路がつながる",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1774790358,
      "updated": 1774790867
    },
    {
      "id": "69c927f600000000001aa190",
      "text": " https://www.google.com/search?q=LLMによるヨイショ",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1774790647,
      "updated": 1774790647
    },
    {
      "id": "69c927f400000000001aa18e",
      "text": " https://www.google.co.jp/search?q=ai+sycophancy&lr=-lang_ja",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1774790644,
      "updated": 1774790679
    },
    {
      "id": "69c9287e0000000000ce3d3f",
      "text": " [AIのおべっか]を使えばいいんだ",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1774790782,
      "updated": 1774790876
    },
    {
      "id": "69c928dc0000000000ce3d44",
      "text": "  全部自分がつけたやつなので変更して大丈夫そう",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1774790876,
      "updated": 1774790879
    },
    {
      "id": "69c928c50000000000ce3d43",
      "text": " どっちも残す",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1774790853,
      "updated": 1774790900
    },
    {
      "id": "69c928f40000000000ce3d48",
      "text": "  せっかく自然発生したので",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1774790900,
      "updated": 1774790905
    }
  ]
}